0:
”Alexa, ask Asheville Vegan for a fact”
”Alexa, ask Asheville Vegan to give me a fact”

skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: asheville vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in and around Asheville, North Carolina. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Asheville Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Asheville Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
